## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- Node.js >= 20.9.0
{{#if (eq packageManager "pnpm")}}
- pnpm
{{else if (eq packageManager "yarn")}}
- Yarn
{{else if (eq packageManager "bun")}}
- Bun
{{/if}}
- Git

### Setup

1. Fork the repository
2. Clone your fork:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/{{projectName}}.git
   cd {{projectName}}
   ```

3. Install dependencies:
   ```bash
{{#if (eq packageManager "pnpm")}}
   pnpm install
{{else if (eq packageManager "yarn")}}
   yarn install
{{else if (eq packageManager "bun")}}
   bun install
{{else}}
   npm install
{{/if}}
   ```

4. Create a branch:
   ```bash
   git checkout -b feature/your-feature-name
   ```

