## Code Style

{{#if typescript}}
### TypeScript

- Use strict TypeScript
- Prefer interfaces over types for object shapes
- Use type inference when possible
- Avoid `any` type unless absolutely necessary

{{/if}}
{{#if (eq styling "tailwind")}}
### Styling

- Use Tailwind CSS utility classes
- Follow mobile-first responsive design
- Use consistent spacing (Tailwind spacing scale)

{{/if}}
### React Best Practices

- Use functional components and hooks
- Keep components small and focused
- Use meaningful component and variable names
- Add JSDoc comments for complex logic
- Prefer composition over inheritance

{{#if (eq backend "firebase")}}
### Firebase

- Never expose Firebase Admin credentials to client
- Use security rules for client-side operations
- Validate all data on the server
- Handle errors appropriately

{{/if}}
